@startuml
title Proxy - Ejemplo 1 - Implementacion Generica
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class Proxy {
    +request(): void
  }
  class RealSubject {
    +request(): void
  }
  interface Subject <<interfaz>> {
  }
}

Subject <|.. Proxy
Subject <|.. RealSubject
Proxy ..> RealSubject : crea
Subject ..> RealSubject : crea
Main ..> Proxy : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
